                        <GroupBox Header="Help &amp; About">

                            <FlowDocumentScrollViewer>
                                <FlowDocument Name="AboutFlowDocument">

                                    <Paragraph>
                                        <Run FontSize="16"
                                                FontWeight="Bold">Star Citizen In-Game Radio Panel</Run>
                                    </Paragraph>
                                    <Paragraph FontSize="14">
                                        Star Citizen does not allow any windows to appear on top of it when in Full Screen Mode. We recommend that you run the game in WINDOWED mode to get around this limitation.
                                    </Paragraph>

                                    <Paragraph>
                                        <Run FontSize="16"
                                                FontWeight="Bold">SRS Standard Operating Procedures (SOP)</Run>
                                    </Paragraph>
                                    <Paragraph FontSize="14">
                                        The Vanguard SRS SOP can be found
                                        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://www.profile.vngd.net/wings/command/library/3be21dcb-d0cd-4793-9890-64f0462776a9/srs-radio-sop-%26-training-manual">here,</Hyperlink>
                                        as well as on the vngd.net website under the Command Library section.
                                    </Paragraph>

                                    <Paragraph>
                                        <Run FontSize="16"
                                                FontWeight="Bold">Vanguard SRS Server Information</Run>
                                    </Paragraph>
                                    <Paragraph FontSize="14">
                                        The Vanguard SRS server information can be found on the Vanguard website or in the Vanguard Discord channel
                                        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://discord.com/channels/491511591402209281/1151272629886529536">#srs-status</Hyperlink>
                                        .
                                    </Paragraph>

                                    <Paragraph>
                                        <Run FontSize="16"
                                                FontWeight="Bold">Speaker and Microphone Boost</Run>
                                    </Paragraph>

                                    <Paragraph FontSize="14">
                                        <Run FontSize="14"
                                                FontWeight="Bold">Please preview your audio first</Run>
                                        using the preview option to make sure that your microphone and speakers are configured correctly.
                                    </Paragraph>

                                    <Paragraph FontSize="14">
                                        Speaker boost can be set higher to counteract the volume reduction caused by clipping and the radio effects. If speaker boost is too high - you may have issues where other windows sounds are too loud. Reduce the boost to fix this.
                                    </Paragraph>

                                    <Paragraph>
                                        <Run FontSize="16"
                                                FontWeight="Bold">Troubleshooting</Run>
                                    </Paragraph>

                                    <Paragraph FontSize="14">
                                        If you have any issues with the SRS please get help on the
                                        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://discord.com/channels/491511591402209281/1151272629886529536">#srs-status</Hyperlink>
                                        channel under the
                                        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://discord.com/channels/491511591402209281/1153198228607610981">SRS Training &amp; Support</Hyperlink>
                                        thread on the
                                        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://discord.gg/GDadyHz">Vanguard discord server.</Hyperlink>
                                    </Paragraph>

                                    <Paragraph>
                                        <Run FontSize="16"
                                                FontWeight="Bold">Input Device not detected?</Run>
                                    </Paragraph>
                                    <Paragraph FontSize="14">
